examination_example.sentence: Aristocrat's country houses all had Roman-style <highlight>gardens</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 贵族的乡间别墅都有罗马式的花园。

examination_example.sentence: Italian architects were hired to design houses and <highlight>gardens</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 意大利建筑师被雇来设计房屋和花园。
